<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1437,187,392]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,449,295,320]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">General distribution.</emphasis>
This is mainly a southeastern species distributed from Pennsylvania to Florida and west to Mississippi and Louisiana.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1437,187,392]" box="[197,1328,367,392]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">
